  "text": "Over time researchers have tried to describe and measure personality traits (individual tendencies to react emotionally or behaviorally in a specific way) using various tests. The most popular model is the \"Big Five\" model that describes five personality traits [CITATION_1] : Neuroticism (N), extroversion (E), openness (0), Agreeableness (A), and conscientiousness (C).",
